title: Fat Joe Interview and More
itunes:title: Fat Joe Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had Fat Joe where he talked about new music, bullying, and squashing 50 Cent and Ja Rule's beef. Yee also takes phone calls and helps people out with their relationship and career struggles during "Ask Yee" and Donkey of the Day goes to KFC for releasing a donut chicken sandwich.
